Signed-off-by: Mark Brown <broonie@kernel.org>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 sound/soc/intel/boards/sof_nau8825.c           | 18 +-----------------
 .../intel/common/soc-acpi-intel-rpl-match.c    |  6 +++---
